snippet.title: V1RUZ - Official Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1140460/V1RUZ/

Hey everyone! Today we are proud to announce V1RUZ, a top-down survival game in a post apocalyptic world filled with zombies! 

Join our Discord to follow the game's development and join our community!
Discord Link: https://discord.gg/mFJRZ8b
